snippet: After waiting 20 years to meet in the playoffs, the Los Angeles Kings and Anaheim Ducks provided an overtime thriller in the opening tussle for Southern California supremacy....

headline.print_headline: Gaborik Leads Kings to 3-2 OT Win vs Ducks
headline.main: Gaborik Leads Kings to 3-2 OT Win vs Ducks

lead_paragraph: After waiting 20 years to meet in the playoffs, the Los Angeles Kings and Anaheim Ducks provided an overtime thriller in the opening tussle for Southern California supremacy.
